Rating: 4
Yummy; everyone loved it! I did make a couple of changes. I too, don't like raisins with pears so I used sweetened dried cranberries. They were perfect. I served the crumble with the new Dreamery ice cream, Dulce de Leche--just right. Why bother with the Cruisnart when the topping can be made with pie crust blender and then used instantly?

